HEADWORD: Youngster
<hw>Young"ster</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A young person; a
youngling; a lad.</def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧He felt himself
quite a <xex>youngster</xex>, with a long life before him.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>G. Eliot.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
